latestPosts.caption:
One year already?

I still remember my on-site interview — I was so nervous, thinking “ki is baar bhi nahi ho payega” (yes, it was my third attempt at Deloitte). After waiting anxiously for 2-3 days, I finally got a call from HR saying, “You’re selected!” In that moment, all my nervousness just disappeared because I had made it to the Big 4. Yes, the Big 4!

The younger version of Seema is really proud today. We’ve come such a long way🥹🥹🧿
